Shisha.Network helps you find nearby top-rated restaurants, bars and cafes with genuine ratings and reviews by customers.Whether you are looking for best offers or discovering new experiences in your area or any other city or country!

The app allows you to set your location to any area whether inside the country or outside to access special offers or deals specific to the location.

Shisha.Network will make it easy for you to discover new places with quick access to the menus, contact information, location, driving directions, and operating hours.

Navigate through featured offers and happy hour offers to choose the best deal at the right location and time!

Our advanced search option with filters and map locations will let you find exactly what you are looking for.

Shisha.Network encourages interactivity with your friends by finding and sharing places.

The community feature in the app is a space where you can add your friends, remember their birthdays and send coins as gifts to the members of your community.

Share your preferred spots, view highlighted reviews from your friends

You will get welcome bonus coins once registered, additional coins for referral ID, and coins can be sent or received in the community page with your friends 

Stay tuned for offers that can be redeemed with coins 

Access great deals and discounts
